  "hint": "Chain three transistors in series: T1(ctrl=A, data=B) outputs A·B. T2(ctrl=C, data=T1) outputs A·B·C. T3(ctrl=D, data=T2) outputs A·B·C·D. Only when every control is HIGH does the signal reach the output.",
